            <title>[LU-3565] HSM: Allow specifying minimum FID sequence at format time</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3565</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In order to allow importing an existing HSM archive into a newly-formatted MDT filesystem, it is necessary to specify a minimum FID SEQ value at mkfs.lustre time for MDT0000 so that these SEQ values will not be reused.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
